Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您经常来这家店吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被治愈了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  这家店很棒  女仆们也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很棒的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还有什么吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:22.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（把重要的魔法忘得一干二净的田中理惠）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…可以允许我为您施放让食物美味三倍的魔法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  有什么事吗  主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有这种动作的魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:38.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（全忘了…）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  「萌啊  萌啊  啾～」的魔法可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
