Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变美味～变美味～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌啊  萌啊  啾～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪啊闪啊闪啊闪～～
