Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您的点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是田中理惠小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（您是田中理惠小姐吧？）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:09:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢玛莉亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:03.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（我最喜欢玛莉亚了!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请蛮…请慢用  告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记施魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位客人「啊？这就走了？」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘干净了  忘干净了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  主人  欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:29.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（今天最后的主人!!）
