Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
