Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑眯眯的～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L O V E～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再画一个心～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以允许我为您施放让食物变美味的魔法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  这样应该会美味一百万倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变美味～变美味～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌啊  萌啊  啾～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪啊闪啊闪啊闪～～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:12:01.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（POPOPURE女仆全体集合!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样食物就美味一百倍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[刚才明明说的是一百万倍吧喂…]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么主人  请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:32.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（今天的感想如何？）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天十分开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但的确有点辛苦  女仆的工作真是辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受点餐  还有…在这家店还要施放魔法什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施放魔法的时候还真是相当紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有机会画画了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:57.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（画得怎么样？）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  画得不错  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画了心形的脸  还写了Love
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画得很漂亮  连我自己都吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:11.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（接近玛莉亚的境界了吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…较玛莉亚还是有很大差距  只是稍微学会了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:22.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（请给今天的女仆体验打个分吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  能打多少分呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100分吗？感谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女仆前辈们给我打了100分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得自己做得还远远不够  以为也就能得一半50分左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:48.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（辛苦了）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈女仆们做得都十分漂亮  可我却因为不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有些对不起大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳烦大家的地方真是十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:14:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们下次再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是扮演玛莉亚的田中理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见


